<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>git on atamanroman.dev</title><link>https://www.atamanroman.dev/tags/git/</link><description>Recent content in git on atamanroman.dev</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Aug 2020 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.atamanroman.dev/tags/git/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Change Your Git User Depending on the Current Directory with Conditional Includes</title><link>https://www.atamanroman.dev/links/change-git-user-depending-current-directory-conditional-include/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 Aug 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.atamanroman.dev/links/change-git-user-depending-current-directory-conditional-include/</guid><description>&lt;p>Git 2.13+ introduced &lt;a href="https://git-scm.com/docs/git-config#_conditional_includes">&lt;em>Conditional Includes&lt;/em>&lt;/a> which allow to set the Git user name depending on the Git repo directory (and much more):&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;width:auto;overflow:auto;display:block;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2">&lt;code>&lt;span style="margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="color:#666">[&lt;/span>includeIf &lt;span style="color:#b44">&amp;#34;gitdir:~/code/&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#666">]&lt;/span>
&lt;span style="color:#b8860b">path&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#666">=&lt;/span> .gitconfig-personal
&lt;span style="color:#666">[&lt;/span>includeIf &lt;span style="color:#b44">&amp;#34;gitdir:~/code/work/&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#666">]&lt;/span>
&lt;span style="color:#b8860b">path&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#666">=&lt;/span> .gitconfig-work
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
